26 law of the jurisdiction in which the debtor is located governs both of the following:
27 (1) Perfection of a security interest in a controllable account, controllable
28 electronic record, or controllable payment intangible by filing.
29 (2) Automatic perfection of a security interest in a controllable payment
30 intangible created by a sale of the controllable payment intangible."
